      "side": 1,
      "message": "Line 110: forEach() invokes user-provided callbacks while holding the registry mutex. If the callback calls back into the registry, this deadlocks; if it does slow work, all registry operations are blocked. Snapshot the entries under the lock, release it, then invoke callbacks.\n```suggestion\nstd::vector\u003cstd::pair\u003cstd::string, std::shared_ptr\u003cNetworkSimulator\u003e\u003e\u003e entries;\n{\n    std::lock_guard lock(mutex_);\n    entries.assign(simulators_.begin(), simulators_.end());\n}\nfor (const auto\u0026 [key, sim] : entries) {\n    auto sep \u003d key.find(\u0027:\u0027);\n    if (sep !\u003d std::string::npos)\n        cb(key.substr(0, sep), key.substr(sep + 1), sim);\n}\n```",
      "revId": "5ab20db455e57bc0c4f0a98f6e3543f86b50e493",
